  <entry>
    <title>Flutter相关简介及环境配置</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/10/11/Flutter%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B%E5%8F%8A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/10/11/Flutter相关简介及环境配置/</id>
    <published>2019-10-11T11:57:45.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-15T10:06:58.913Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><p>18年2月份提出概念，</p></li><li><p>6月份上线正式使用 </p></li><li><p>12月5日正式发布1.0版本</p><p>  <a href="https://book.flutterchina.club/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Flutter中文网参考</a></p></li></ul><h3 id="相关技术简介"><a href="#相关技术简介" class="headerlink" title="相关技术简介"></a>相关技术简介</h3><h4 id="原生开发简介"><a href="#原生开发简介" class="headerlink" title="原生开发简介"></a>原生开发简介</h4><p>iOS：Objective-C或Swift语言调用iOS SDK<br>Android:Java或Kotlin语言直接调用Android SDK</p><p>优势：可访问平台全部功能（GPS、摄像头）；<br>    速度快、性能高、可以实现复杂动画及绘制，整体用户体验好；</p><p>缺点：平台特定，开发成本高；不同平台必须维护不同代码，人力成本随之变大；<br>    内容固定，动态化弱，大多数情况下，有新功能更新时只能发版；</p><p>纯原生开发的问题：<br>    动态化内容需求增大<br>    业务需求变化快，开发成本变大</p><h4 id="跨平台技术简介"><a href="#跨平台技术简介" class="headerlink" title="跨平台技术简介"></a>跨平台技术简介</h4><p>1、H5+原生（Cordova、Ionic、微信小程序）webview<br>    通过原生的网页加载控件WebView (Android)或WKWebView（ios）来加载<br>    我们称这种h5+原生的开发模式为混合开发 ，采用混合模式开发的APP我们称之为混合应用或Hybird APP ，<br>    如果一个应用的大多数功能都是H5实现的话，我们称其为Web APP 。<br>    WebView是JavaScript与原生API之间通信的桥梁，<br>    传输协议的工具称之为WebView JavaScript Bridge, 简称 JsBridge（核心）</p><p>2、JavaScript开发+原生渲染 （React Native、Weex、快应用）<br>    采用Web开发技术栈，社区庞大、上手快、开发成本相对较低。<br>    原生渲染，性能相比H5提高很多。<br>    动态化较好，支持热更新。</p><p>3、自绘UI+原生(QT for mobile、Flutter)<br>    通过在不同平台实现一个统一接口的渲染引擎来绘制UI，而不依赖系统原生控件<br>    所以可以做到不同平台UI的一致性，注意，自绘引擎解决的是UI的跨平台问题，<br>    如果涉及其它系统能力调用，依然要涉及原生开发（调取摄像头等系统设备）</p><p>具体跨平台技术介绍<br>    Ionic：angelur常用的组件库（官网：ionicframework.com）<br>    快应用：中国的Android手机厂商联合推出的类似于rn的技术<br>    Weex：阿里的kpi项目（不维护了）vue开发<br>    微信小程序：在webview中渲染的，并非原生渲染，但将来有可能原生渲染</p><h3 id="flutter简介"><a href="#flutter简介" class="headerlink" title="flutter简介"></a>flutter简介</h3><p><strong>跨平台自绘引擎</strong></p><p>跨平台自会引擎，flutter与用于构建移动应用程序的大多数框架不同，因为flutter即不使用WebView，<br>也不使用操作系统的原生控件，相反，flutter使用自己的高性能渲染引擎来绘制widget</p><p><strong>高性能(JIT和AOT)</strong></p><p>AOT（Ahead of time）:静态编译的程序在执行前全部被翻译为机器码(提前编译)<br>JIT（Just-in-time）:解释执行的则是一句一句边翻译边运行(即时编译)</p><p><strong>为什么采用Dart开发</strong></p><p>1、开发效率高<br>2、高性能<br>3、快速内存分配<br>4、类型安全<br>5、Dart团队就在隔壁</p><h3 id="环境搭建"><a href="#环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="环境搭建"></a>环境搭建</h3><h4 id="安装开发环境"><a href="#安装开发环境" class="headerlink" title="安装开发环境"></a>安装开发环境</h4><p>1、安装Flutter SDK（Mac）<br><a href="https://flutter.io/docs/development/tools/sdk/archive" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://flutter.io/docs/development/tools/sdk/archive</a></p><ul><li>下载解压，压缩包放到应用程序里</li><li>配置环境变量： ~/.bash_profile<br>添加：export PATH=$PATH:/Applications/flutter/bin</li><li>执行 source ~/.bash_profile</li><li>flutter –help</li></ul><p>2、配置iOS开发环境（Mac）</p><ul><li>安装xcode</li><li>启动模拟器</li><li>配置VS Code<br>安装 flutter扩展</li></ul><p>3、检测问题</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; flutter doctor</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>问题1：Android license status unknown<br>&emsp;&emsp;找到 sdk/tools/bin 下的sdkmanager.bat    %DEFAULT_JVM_OPTS%  后面添加 -XX:+IgnoreUnrecognizedVMOptions –add-modules java.se.ee<br>&emsp;&emsp;flutter doctor –android-licenses<br>&emsp;&emsp;提示问题后升级：/usr/local/Cellar/android-sdk/tools/bin/sdkmanager –update<br>问题2：<br>? libimobiledevice and ideviceinstaller are not installed. To install with Brew, run:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew update</span><br><span class="line">brew install --HEAD usbmuxd</span><br><span class="line">brew link usbmuxd</span><br><span class="line">brew install --HEAD libimobiledevice</span><br><span class="line">brew install ideviceinstaller</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>? ios-deploy not installed. To install with Brew:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install ios-deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>? CocoaPods not installed.<br>CocoaPods is used to retrieve the iOS platform side’s plugin code that responds to your plugin usage on the Dart side.<br>Without resolving iOS dependencies with CocoaPods, plugins will not work on iOS.<br>For more info, see <a href="https://flutter.io/platform-plugins" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://flutter.io/platform-plugins</a><br>To install:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install cocoapods</span><br><span class="line">pod setup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>问题3：<br>Android Studio (version 3.0)<br>? Flutter plugin not installed; this adds Flutter specific functionality.<br>? Dart plugin not installed; this adds Dart specific functionality.<br>&emsp;&emsp;打开android studio, configure &gt; plugins &gt; 搜索安装 dart, flutter</p><h4 id="创建项目"><a href="#创建项目" class="headerlink" title="创建项目"></a>创建项目</h4><p>1、Using Flutter in China<br>export PUB_HOSTED_URL=<a href="https://pub.flutter-io.cn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pub.flutter-io.cn</a> export FLUTTER_STORAGE_BASE_URL=<a href="https://storage.flutter-io.cn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://storage.flutter-io.cn</a><br>执行 source ~/.bash_profile<br>2、创建<br>flutter create gp7_flutter<br>3、运行flutter项目</p><ul><li>xcode里打开模拟器</li><li>android studio 配置AVD</li><li>flutter emulators</li><li>flutter emulators –launch Nexus_6P_API_28</li><li>flutter run</li></ul><h4 id="快速入门"><a href="#快速入门" class="headerlink" title="快速入门"></a>快速入门</h4><p>1、hello world</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">'package:flutter/material.dart'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> main() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  runApp(</span><br><span class="line">    Center(</span><br><span class="line">      child: Text(</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">'hello world'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        textDirection: TextDirection.ltr</span><br><span class="line">      ),</span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br><span class="line">  );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2、自定义部件(widget)</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">'package:flutter/material.dart'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> main() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  runApp(App());</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">App</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">StatelessWidget</span> 